name: TouhouEnemyModels
description: [SekibankiSpringMan] is deprecated and changed to [TouhouEnemyModels]. This mod replaces the model of enemies with Touhou characters(modified) and also adds their theme music(shortened). All configurable. CoilHead -> Sekibanki, Nutcracker -> Satori, ForestGiant -> Suika, RadMech -> Utsuho, ...
